{"h946139e1gd701g4f17g9cbbg2446d7347ca1": ["*Chirp!*", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "0acb3e45-1620-466f-68ce-5e3c50df03bb"], "h4b66c20fgafe0g454bg8dcag7b9852dde931": ["*The bird is singing as loud as his lungs will allow, practicing fervently.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "b64664c7-0ed5-0b8a-4c73-fecbdee6f7ac"], "h3a0c331eg1511g47fcga719g98239b00bbd7": ["*The bird hops around, scanning sticks and flowers, looking for a nice addition to his nest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "714e4411-18ae-84c8-afd2-aed83613a98b"], "hc13794b5g49e2g41b7gb6dag6ce5873be46e": ["No, no - where is it? I put the coin right here.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "5251fb07-5b05-512e-9ccf-898a635190d1"], "hedb8d53ag0af2g4481g862fg0e3f24f02e57": ["Don't you <i>dare</i>.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "f5840cb8-4e7f-6bc7-4e1e-52e93f41c34a"], "h86f52b63g21d7g4d0cg901agd7e9723260f4": ["Yes... yes, this is perfect.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "2331fec8-f743-3c18-54b9-cb17581e3ec2"], "hbd521d0fg729dg4aecga962g3b51c6c4212e": ["Shh, I'm concentrating. Does this look good? Is the coin in the middle?", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "54219741-37e0-440c-18e8-266312b1cd10"], "h2df5398dg4ddcg4f78ga872g3299969e3b3f": ["It's slightly off - push it a bit to the right.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "f83bc309-44ef-2039-e9db-23d97ea02c76"], "hecb0c72dg9380g4b38gbe9bg1a6158e94296": ["Yes... yes, you're right. That's it.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "f8475ca3-4440-d241-3fea-36d4f4ccfcd9"], "h38135a15ge9b4g41edgb91dg296fd4657db2": ["Stop fussing. It looks fine.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "368aa6ce-91d7-bc03-4401-3a420c1b9b5a"], "ha303aef8g0112g49c4g9e1fg796474aedbc5": ["No... it's leaning too much to the left. Yeah, that's it.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "f126e8b3-2ff8-5eae-3800-f089f6c1a56f"], "ha66b782dgb16ag4bbcgbaa6ga03bdc76c3fd": ["I'd leave it out - it's too dull.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "f31c7ac8-76bd-9863-bd40-843d5a0b9903"], "hb5b796e4g9d1eg4d65g99b6gef82cf504fb1": ["Hmm. Hmmmm...", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "827f89db-14ce-52de-3aba-16340c8c1396"], "h756d31b8g0b36g4496g8c8ag954dadca467b": ["Yeah... yeah, you're right. This is better.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "7813fc9c-41cc-498c-a8c1-d20d7e599ef5"], "hd7a87d95g5313g42b2g9023g64f269dea135": ["It's not. And you better keep those fingers far away.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "fe0a1663-2777-8945-a7ca-09c7638cfd34"], "h88900540gbf10g4e3eg8f48ga5a649feadbd": ["<i>Kick at the bird, trying to scare it away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "741da10b-b7a5-4e3b-79cf-c90cefc786dc"], "hecb56527g01b9g4a7egb4d3g7642259a6ebe": ["Stop it! Help - help!", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "a01d2cdb-d02b-52a9-7136-a0d5d3537e67"], "h63830e19ge5abg4962g8493g19bc3adb0ecc": ["No you <i>don't</i>.", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "739dea15-509f-62d5-27ea-d1e06843cb25"], "h81c55f53g6621g4992gbe3eg33b325050e7f": ["Leave it out - the metal's bad quality. It'll turn green very quickly.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "66abb536-fd50-187d-9c40-721ee7cab336"], "hf64d5c5cg5b86g4bdcg801bg96a2ff01b588": ["Ladies aren't interested in a shiny nest. You should work on your song.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "3f19c94d-fc91-e3d4-a3a9-8f85421098f5"], "h0e74de9egc3ceg4f77gb5a0gfdfcfca50eae": ["Ah, umm... ", "72bd7f25-0644-4323-a428-85ba5630e6ea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "a89b53f7-c804-263a-f317-89e9a2f8a870"], "h3757b39age2c0g469egb3dbgabd241c5015c": ["*He lets out a tentative chirp. Gaining confidence, he starts a song, abandoning his nest-building efforts.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "ff717b9c-af62-bdb2-db7c-1601a23886d1"], "hadfecd16ge222g473eg95d7g88b6518d252e": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_003.html", "7d3540bc-3461-6a38-98c8-c387d171b3c6"]}